headline: FINN Partners Promotes Nicole Janok to Senior Partner Amid Record Growth in Florida
summary: FINN Partners, one of the world's leading independent marketing and communications agencies, today announced the promotion of Nicole Janok to Senior Partner from Partner. In her expanded leadership role, Janok will continue to head the Florida office and serve as a senior advisor in the agency's Purpose and Social Impact Practice.
